# Day 47 – Content Intelligence Studio

## Overview
Built a premium single-page **Content Intelligence Studio** that helps analyze content quality using AI-inspired workflows. The application provides structured content evaluation, recommendations, platform-specific insights, and an interactive dashboard.

## Features
- AI Content Analysis Dashboard
- Multi-stage Content Review Workflow
- Overall Content Score
- Category-wise Analysis
- Strengths & Weaknesses
- Improvement Recommendations
- Alternative Hooks & Titles
- Publishing Checklist
- Executive Summary
- Responsive Dark UI

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

## Learning Outcomes
- Designed an AI-inspired content review workflow
- Built a modern dashboard UI
- Improved responsive design skills
- Organized structured AI feedback visually
- Practiced creating reusable frontend components

